            ><div class="ikmIq9PoTyXOyIgR7" data-instant-type="accordion-content" style="--instant-accordion-content-height:auto;--instant-accordion-content-width:auto"
              ><div data-instant-type="text" class="instant-rich-text i5nHgPynU8i5uDv21"><p>Yes, you can answer and dial calls with your Carbinox Blaze. Just pair it with your phone and make sure Bluetooth is on.</p></div></div
